{"tid":1154341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街！日本Uniqlo及GU購物網站被入侵 46萬顧客個人資料及信用卡外洩！","createTime":"2019-05-14T08:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T09:30:30.000Z","uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8b0aead953c07762f933a48df96904282f0cfe68","tid":1154341,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7094738ef00344dd0189edb8052d3353b04136","tid":1154341,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:35:16.000Z","msg":"日本連鎖服裝品牌UNIQLO母公司迅銷有限公司周二公佈集團網絡被黑客入侵，UNIQLO及平價姊妹品牌GU的購物網站上有46萬1091名客戶資料，可能被未獲授權的單位截取。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，購物網站於上月23日及本月10日被入侵。外洩的資料包括顧客名稱、住址、電話號碼及信用卡資料，客戶如在其他網站使用相同的登入名稱及密碼，需要更改密碼。"},{"pid":"e75a554fe91bf6ec5c6b380a446dc939f66a7113","tid":1154341,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:36:27.000Z","msg":"會唔會係樓主作新聞屈日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52521606a791b112fe308a576942287fb43c6cfd","tid":1154341,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e75a554fe91bf6ec5c6b380a446dc939f66a7113","tid":1154341,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:36:27.000Z","msg":"會唔會係樓主作新聞屈日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:37:43.000Z","msg":"Uniqlo hack: 460,000 accounts compromised on Japanese sites of Asia&rsquo;s biggest retailer<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/east-asia/article/3010100/uniqlo-hack-460000-accounts-compromised-japanese-sites-asias\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fasia%2Feast-asia%2Farticle%2F3010100%2Funiqlo-hack-460000-accounts-compromised-japanese-sites-asias&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=f1d505e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/east-asia/a